g.text: EXPANDING YOUR AWARENESS AROUND WHATS ESSENTIAL FOR GOOD HEALTH

As a qualified nutritionist from Nutrition Institute, I believe that good health requires all things Nature and Nature provides us with a Feast of its own, hence where “Nature’s Feast” came from. My approach is to work one on one, with a person or a whole family in order to discover what is happening, what is missing and where and how do we start to potentially better our lives and lives of the people around us.
